  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playable Characters:</strong> 16 unique heroes with 19 <strong>attributes</strong>  to modify.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pets:</strong> 8 loyal companions to collect (yes pets can <strong>level up</strong>  and get <strong>attacks</strong>)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Levels:</strong> 6 full levels plus a challenging boss dungeon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong> 4 modes that completely change the gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Achievements:</strong> Over 90 achievements to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrades:</strong> 22 unique upgrades with 60+ levels in total</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Attacks:</strong> 37 unique attacks, 5 powerful evolutions, and 16 hero-specific abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Defensive Power-Ups:</strong> 20 different boosts to help you survive</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bosses:</strong> 47 formidable bosses, with 17 featuring unique moves and attack patterns</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game about <strong>love</strong>. (The warm, fuzzy kind. Also the \"whoops, I got smacked\" kind.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/d27619ddc93c1018b0d2a4d7b4e7313c.poster.avif?t=1771055492\" aria-label=\"A game about love. (The warm, fuzzy kind. Also the \"whoops, I got smacked\" kind.)\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/d27619ddc93c1018b0d2a4d7b4e7313c.webm?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/d27619ddc93c1018b0d2a4d7b4e7313c.mp4?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game about <strong>visiting hell</strong>. (Travel insurance not included.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/b65da22752b726c88b9cd7d19c130f22.poster.avif?t=1771055492\" aria-label=\"A game about visiting hell. (Travel insurance not included.)\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/b65da22752b726c88b9cd7d19c130f22.webm?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/b65da22752b726c88b9cd7d19c130f22.mp4?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game about <strong>going farming</strong>. (Grow veggies. Reap gold. Fend off demonic chickens.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/fe8413534b60c50cbe9b3413f719db4b.poster.avif?t=1771055492\" aria-label=\"A game about going farming. (Grow veggies. Reap gold. Fend off demonic chickens.)\" width=550 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/fe8413534b60c50cbe9b3413f719db4b.webm?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/fe8413534b60c50cbe9b3413f719db4b.mp4?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game about <strong>achieving much</strong>. (Mostly bragging rights. Also swords.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/f92988c9a6d1ee17c4b4aa941a96e242.poster.avif?t=1771055492\" aria-label=\"A game about achieving much. (Mostly bragging rights. Also swords.)\" width=550 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/f92988c9a6d1ee17c4b4aa941a96e242.webm?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/f92988c9a6d1ee17c4b4aa941a96e242.mp4?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game about <strong>spending gold</strong>. (The more you buy, the better you get. That’s how economics works, right?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/b1d83b1867a02d5c34c41b0c43d23c9f.poster.avif?t=1771055492\" aria-label=\"A game about spending gold. (The more you buy, the better you get. That’s how economics works, right?)\" width=550 height=550 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/b1d83b1867a02d5c34c41b0c43d23c9f.webm?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2844300/extras/b1d83b1867a02d5c34c41b0c43d23c9f.mp4?t=1771055492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
